Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ơ...?{Huh...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,18:00 có mặt tại trụ sở, nhanh lên.{You need to be at headquarters by 18:00. Hurry.}
